elements.name: User can add product in shopping cart from Laptops & Notebooks menu

steps.name: I am on homepage
I mouse hover on “Laptops & Notebooks”
I click on “Show All Laptops & Notebooks"
I change the currency to "£" from "$"
I sort by "Price (High > Low)"
I select product “MacBook”
I click on 'Add To cart' button
I click on “shopping cart” display into success message
I Change Quantity From "1" to "2"
I Click on update
I Click on checkout button
I Click on “Guest Checkout” radio button
I Click on “continue” tab
I filled the required information
